title: HOUR 1- Peter King Oct 05, 2020
itunes:title: HOUR 1- Peter King Oct 05, 2020
description:
In this hour of The Dan Patrick Show, Peter King of Football Morning in America and NBCSports.com stops in to share his insights on Week 4 of the NFL. Also, Dan knows Jimmy Butler and the Miami Heat won't exit the NBA Finals without a fight. Plus, the Dallas Cowboys have no defense, therefore they have no shot at the playoffs.
